* &quot;UNDA&quot;, with Sue Finlay and Nicholas Sloan, San Diego, Stuart Collection, 1987
* Furka Pass, Switzerland, 1987
* Strasbourg, France, Musée d&#x27;Art Moderne or Musée des Beaux-Arts, 1988
