* &quot;Ovid wall&quot;, &quot;Aphrodite herm&quot;, tree-plaque, &quot;capital&quot;, with Nicholas Sloan, Luton, England, Stockwood Park, 1991
* &quot;tree-plaque&quot;, Hennef, Germany, private garden, 1991
